g\u002Ftennis",us:cA,nl:"\u002Fnl\u002Ftennis",mx:"\u002Fmx\u002Ftenis",fr:"\u002Ffr\u002Ftennis"},seo:{title:cE,description:jX,keywords:e,template:{heading:e,short_description:e,full_description:"{TAB title=Scores}\u003Ch1\u003ELive tennis scores - latest matches and today's results\u003C\u002Fh1\u003E\u003Ch2 id=\"tennis-live-scores\"\u003ETennis live scores\u003C\u002Fh2\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHere at Oddspedia, we know just how important it is to stay up to date and in the know when it comes to tennis live scores. That’s why we give you everything from the latest tennis tournaments, detailed stats from the matches as they happen and when the players are on the court. Our tennis live scores cover every type of pro tennis match and tournament big or small. \u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou can find tennis scores today from pro circuit events like the ATP and WTP tour. Of course, we extensively cover the grand slam tournaments of \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Foddspedia.com\u002Fus\u002Ftennis\u002Funited-kingdom\u002Fatp-wimbledon\"\u003EWimbledon\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, the \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Foddspedia.com\u002Fus\u002Ftennis\u002Fusa\u002Fatp-us-open\"\u003EUS Open\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, the \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Foddspedia.com\u002Fus\u002Ftennis\u002Faustralia\u002Fatp-australian-open\"\u003EAustralian Open\u003C\u002Fa\u003E and the \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Foddspedia.com\u002Ftennis\u002Ffrance\u002Fatp-french-open\"\u003EFrench Open\u003C\u002Fa\u003E. We even have you covered for the Challenger Tour to see who the next rising star might be. \u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Ch2 id=\"tennis-matches-today\"\u003ETennis matches today\u003C\u002Fh2\u003E\u003Cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003EOur group of tennis betting experts take immense pride in curating the most comprehensive live scores for tennis. Our objective goes beyond just informing you about the current match winner; we strive to provide a wealth of additional data. Our meticulous approach ensures that you stay informed about crucial aspects of the game, such as the number of aces hit, double faults served, and the serving positions of the players (whether it's the ad court or deuce court).\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003EOn top of this, we offer you the historical context of the fixture between the two players, presenting their previous encounters' outcomes in a lucid manner. By incorporating the players' current ATP world rankings, we enable you to gauge the favored contender and understand why the pre-match odds might be inclined towards a particular outcome. Moreover, our search bar feature allows you to effortlessly access all the ongoing tennis live scores and upcoming matches, filtering out irrelevant matches with utmost convenience. With Oddspedia, you'll be equipped with the most intricate and up-to-date information to enhance your tennis-watching experience.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Ch2 id=\"tennis-stats\"\u003ETennis stats\u003C\u002Fh2\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhile tennis live scores are a great way for you to check in on the progress of a match and to see how your bet is doing, the real beauty lies in these stats themselves. We give you live in-game stats but it's the pregame stats that are going to help you make your decision on which way to go with your bet. \u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,0%);\"\u003EExplore all the intriguing information with our tennis statistics prior to the match getting underway. Review the head-to-head statistics to examine their previous meetings, recent victors, and their present global rankings. Additionally, we provide insights into their current overall performance so you can stay informed about the players entering the match.\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo, what is the relevance of this information? You use the stats that we give you to help you make a more informed decision for your bet. If you see a match that shows a history of one player regularly beating the other then you can play it safe with your bet. If the result history shows that there has been an upset or two in the past, you may decide you want to take a punt on the favorable underdog \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Foddspedia.com\u002Fus\u002Ftennis\u002Fodds\"\u003Etennis odds\u003C\u002Fa\u003E. The choice is yours, we simply provide you with the stats and details to help you make the best decisions. \u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Ch2 id=\"tennis-live-streams\"\u003ETennis live streams\u003C\u002Fh2\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOnce you have identified the player you would like to back, Oddspedia can point you to a free tennis stream where you can easily check the progress of your wager. All you need to do is click on the \"Live Stream\" option on the match and then click \"Watch Your Event Live\". We will do our best to link you to any available real-time streaming of the match. This way, you can watch the match in motion and make sure your bet is a success.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Ch2 id=\"tennis-news\"\u003ETennis news\u003C\u002Fh2\u003E\u003Cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003EAt Oddspedia, our team of experts is dedicated to being your ultimate destination for the most up-to-date tennis news and statistics. With our extensive knowledge and experience, we provide you with in-depth articles that cover all the prominent players, tournaments, and more. Simply select tennis from our sports list, click on 'news,' and immerse yourself in a plethora of free articles featuring the latest tennis events and invaluable information. Our commitment is to offer you comprehensive and timely coverage, effortlessly delivered to your screen.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003EWhile we boast our own talented team of writers, we primarily bring you the freshest tennis news from renowned sports journalism outlets. At Oddspedia, our team of experts diligently sifts through numerous stories, meticulously handpicking the finest pieces t